Class GridNioFilterAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.internal.util.nio.GridNioFilterAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GridNioFilter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GridConnectionBytesVerifyFilter, GridNioAsyncNotifyFilter, GridNioCodecFilter, GridNioFilterChain, GridNioSslFilter

    public abstract class GridNioFilterAdapter
extends Object
implements GridNioFilter
    Class that defines the piece for application-to-network and vice-versa data conversions (protocol transformations, encryption, etc.)
